      "text": "それより{user}さんは\nこんな所で何をしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyways‚ {user}-san‚\nwhat are you doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今、スタジオで打ち合わせが終わって\nその帰り道です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I finished a meeting at the studio‚\nand I’m heading home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 44.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったんですね\n今日もお疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nI guess you had another long day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで、何か押したみたいですけど\n大丈夫でしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ you seem to have pushed a button.\nWas it what you wanted?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n……あ、ああっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nWait‚ what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 53.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 55.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "コーヒー……間違えて押しちゃったみたいです\n私、苦いのって苦手で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Coffee… I pushed the coffee button by mistake.\nI don’t like bitter stuff…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、でもこれって微糖なんですね\n私でも飲めるかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ but this is the low sugar version.\nMaybe even I can drink that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 69.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……奥山さん、良かったらそのコーヒー\n俺がもらってもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s alright with you‚ Okuyama-san‚\nI could take that coffee.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして気を遣ってくれてます？\nえへへ、大丈夫ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you trying to be nice?\nHehehe‚ that’s fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 80.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、俺が急に声を掛けたのが原因ですし\nさあ、好きなのを押して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ but you pressed the wrong button because I spoke to you suddenly.\nSo this time‚ choose the one you like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_money-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 84.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "……ホントに、いいんですか？\n迷惑掛けてませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You really don’t mind?\nI’m not bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "気にし過ぎです\nほら、コーヒーもらいますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re too kind.\nRight‚ so I’ll have that coffee.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 96.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます\nじゃあ、お言葉に甘えて……えいっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you.\nWell‚ since you offered‚ yap.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_canned-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5833.3333333333285,
          "startTime": 102.73333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 104.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、おしるこ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ red bean soup…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 106.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "ジュースかおしるこか、迷ってたんですけど\n甘いのが食べたくなったから、こっちにしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was torn between fruit juice or red bean soup‚\nbut I wanted something sweet‚ so I went for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_sancha-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 112.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "一度食べたら病みつきですよ！\n{user}さんも試してみますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Try it once‚ and you’ll get hooked on this stuff!\nHow about you try some too‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね\n機会があれば食べてみます……はは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That looks nice.\nI’ll try some if I get the chance.",
